# Files NOT to publish as static assets on Cloudflare Pages. The deployed site needs only the
# viewer (index.html, app.js, style.css), the editor (edit.html), the data the browser fetches
# (data/plots.json, data/plot_points.geojson, data/plot_polygons.geojson), tithe.pmtiles, and the
# functions/ (handled separately as Pages Functions, not static assets).
#
# Everything below is either source material, local-only tooling, or docs, and must not be served.
source_images/
scripts/
data/review/
review.html
assist.html
resolve.html
worker.js
wrangler.toml
.gitignore
*.md
